---

<section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-50 via-amber-100 to-amber-50 border-y-2 border-amber-300 px-6 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-amber-300 rounded-full opacity-20 -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-24 h-24 bg-amber-400 rounded-full opacity-20 translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2"></div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-red-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-4 shadow-lg">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 animate-pulse" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
      </svg>
      OFERTA POR TEMPO LIMITADO
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4">Promoção de Lançamento Termina Em Breve</h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-4 shadow-lg border-2 border-amber-300">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-1">Preço de Lançamento</p>
        <p class="text-3xl font-black text-[#2C3E99]">R$ 47</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">ou 3x R$ 15,67</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-4 shadow-lg border border-gray-200 opacity-75">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-1">Preço Normal (após promoção)</p>
        <p class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-400 line-through">R$ 147</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Você economiza R$ 100</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-4 shadow-lg border-2 border-red-200 mb-6 max-w-xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-3">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-red-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
        </svg>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Vagas Limitadas</p>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
        Apenas <strong class="text-red-600 text-lg">100 vagas</strong> com desconto de lançamento.<br/>
        <span class="text-[#4CAF50] font-semibold">87 professoras</span> já garantiram as delas.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-3 bg-gray-200 rounded-full h-3 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-orange-500 h-full rounded-full" style="width: 87%;"></div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 mt-1">Restam apenas <strong class="text-red-600">13 vagas</strong> com este desconto</p>
    </div>

    <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Quando as 100 vagas acabarem, o preço sobe para R$ 147. Não deixe para depois!</p>
  </div>
</section>
